    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079160/extras/e2b2705422b3997fd6c9602e7f09f99c.avif?t=1768508224\" width=800 height=450 /></span> <br>在这款受MMO副本启发的单人动作roguelite中，通过迫使敌人攻击你来保护队伍！创建独特流派，解锁强大天赋，掌握坦克艺术，掌控混乱战场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 吸引敌人的注意力 </h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过伤害敌人来保持仇恨！或者通过奔跑强迫他们攻击你！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't Lose Aggro让你可以扮演任何你能想到的坦克类型，专注于控制、策略和走位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079160/extras/ab267173ee1342a7ca54f7705918fbfd.avif?t=1768508224\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 你的同伴 </h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的任务是保护队伍免受伤害！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同伴在存活时提供强大的可升级技能，这是成功通关的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't Lose Aggro让你选择保护同伴，或者在硬核模式中牺牲他们！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079160/extras/72dcee018ec81fb4e6c8e9dd78649de7.avif?t=1768508224\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 技能 </h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用你的技能成为你想要的坦克类型。冲锋可以缩短你与敌人之间的距离，但如果你偏好慢节奏，也可以把他们拉向你！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部分技能偏向攻击和伤害，而其他技能则专注于保护和治疗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079160/extras/51a8eb41ecd192123d3800cfc6207780.poster.avif?t=1768508224\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079160/extras/51a8eb41ecd192123d3800cfc6207780.webm?t=1768508224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079160/extras/51a8eb41ecd192123d3800cfc6207780.mp4?t=1768508224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 成长系统 </h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过消耗天赋点来升级你的永久坦克流派，匹配你偏好的游戏风格。扮演闪避型、格挡型、风筝型或嘲讽型——每种都有独特的机制和升级路线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 游戏世界 </h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越被熔岩环绕的毁灭之岛，在旋风沙漠的沙暴中求生，在&quot;陨落之城&quot;迎接最终挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着进度推进，你将解锁新的竞技场，与新的敌人和首领战斗，证明你的坦克实力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
